{
  "name": "RoleRadar · 1 · Discover",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📡 RoleRadar — Phase 1 · Discover\n\nScans LinkedIn (free guest endpoint) across the searches in your **Filter** tab, dedupes, and writes new jobs to the sheet.\n\n**In:** `Filter` tab (your keywords)  •  **Out:** `Jobs` tab (status = `New`)\n**Setup:** paste `GOOGLE_SHEET_ID` in **Search Configuration**.\n\n— github.com/damran/role-radar",
        "height": 1004,
        "width": 3168,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "5408ab5e-cb59-4bc5-a6d7-27773a86f9af",
      "name": "RoleRadar Frame",
