        "jsCode": "// Access the static data of the FILTER node specifically\nconst filterNodeName = 'P1: Filter New Jobs Only'; \nconst staticData = $getWorkflowStaticData(filterNodeName);\n\n// Clean wipe\nstaticData.seenIds = [];\nstaticData.seenKeys = [];\nstaticData.seenUrls = [];\n\nreturn $input.all();"
